skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: final grade calculator
des: The Final Grade Calculator Skill will calculate your final grade based on the grades you achieved this following semester / quarter. You have two options: calculate your overall final grade or calculate the grade necessary for an unknown part to achieve a certain grade (i.e. a final, ungraded homework, a quiz). There is a maximum of 6 grades that you may enter to calculate your final grade.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
